And just what is the international strike force called THE UNITED – and why have they marked UNITY’s own X-O Manowar, Ninjak, Livewire, and Eternal Warrior for elimination? Red-hot creators Matt Kindt and CAFU detonate the planet’s first superteam vs. superteam war right here with a bold new beginning for UNITY!

The Ranch of Riddles

In this romantic issue of Cowgirl Romances take a trip back in time to the sweaty plains of the Wild West, where women defended the house and found romance under the stars...

Jessie Hayden's heart becomes entangled in a mysterious web of the cattle kingdom called the "Ranch of Riddles". Stella Dawson, a rodeo entrepreneur, always promised to give'm their money's worth until a new flame came to the show in "Love Rode In". Miss Kitty dreamed of the day her man would return, but when it happens is it as she imagined in "Send Back My Love". A southern bell clings to her old way of life, until romance forces a change in "My Rebel Heart" plus more and vintage advertisements.

Cowgirl Romances combines country beauties, Western villains and good ol' fashioned gun fights. Join the real heroes of the homestead in battles against bandits and for the hearts of hunky cowboys.

Enjoy a nostalgic trip down memory lane with the best titles from the golden age of comics. Yojimbo Press has lovingly remastered these timeless classics with vivid color correction and image restoration.
